snippet.title: Dark and Darker Mobile | Pre-Registration Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you brave enough to answer the call of darkness?
The time has come! Pre-registration for Dark and Darker Mobile is now OPEN! ⚔️ 
Available on Mobile (Android, Galaxy Store, iOS) and PC (Google Play Games)

🔸Pre-Register on iOS & Android: https://bit.ly/DNDM_PreRegisterNow
🔸Pre-Register on our Website: https://dndm.krafton.com

Complete your pre-registration and claim exclusive rewards!
🎁 Limited Edition Golden Mask Skin 
🎁 Tier A Mercenary
🎁 Lv3 Helmet Skin (Earned through our friend invitation special event)

Stay tuned with https://www.youtube.com/@darkanddarkermobile 
👉 Twitter: https://twitter.com/darkanddarker_m
👉 Discord: https://discord.gg/darkanddarkermobile
👉 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/darkanddarkermobile/
👉 TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@darkanddarkermobile
👉 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DarkandDarkerM

#DarkandDarkerMobile #DNDM
